s0价格 vs 交易回报¶

In [279]:
p = 100
group_s0 = pd.DataFrame()
group_s0['avg'] = bt_data.groupby(pd.qcut(bt_data['s0'],p))['rets_bi'].mean()
group_s0['max'] = bt_data.groupby(pd.qcut(bt_data['s0'],p))['rets_bi'].max()
group_s0['min'] = bt_data.groupby(pd.qcut(bt_data['s0'],p))['rets_bi'].min()
group_s0['error'] = group_s0[['max','min']].T.std()
group_s0['series'] = [i for i in range(p)]
group_s0['left'] = group_s0.index.to_frame().apply(lambda x:x['s0'].left,axis=1)
group_s0['right'] = group_s0.index.to_frame().apply(lambda x:x['s0'].right,axis=1)
In [282]:
group_s0.plot(kind='barh',x='right',y='avg',xerr='error',figsize=(12,20),width=1)
